US citizens:
<a href="https://actionnetwork.org/forms/sign-the-petition-revoke-the-nras-tax-exempt-status?nowrapper=true&referrer=group-progress-america&source=2023TaxNRA_PA">call on the IRS</a>
to revoke the National Rifle Association's tax exemption.
<p>
The National Rifle Association used to work dedicate itself to
teaching how to safely use and own guns.  It was turned into a tool for
<a href="https://stallman.org/archives/2014-may-aug.html#5_May_2014_(Poverty_and_guns)">spreading fear to promote gun sales</a>
a few decades ago.

